text: Came here just to see wild boars but no wild boars.

This is a new bus terminal located about 5 minutes walk from Tuas Link MRT station. There is a pedestrian entrance at the bottom of the bus ramp, accessed by stairs or elevator.
There are restrooms, counters, and vending machines inside the terminal. There aren't that many people. You can take a bus to Boon Lay station.
